@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.abs(tmp) - ((v2 + 0.10 + v0 + 0.04) + (v2 + 0.03 + tmp + 0.08)))
    tmp = 0.72
    v0 = (v1 * wp.exp(wp.exp(tmp + 0.56)))
    v2 = (0.49 + (wp.sin(v0 + 0.35) + wp.sin(v0 + 0.01)))
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.cos((v1 + 0.73 * tmp + 0.91)))
    v0 = (((v2 + 0.55 + v2 + 0.47) / (v0 + 0.52 - v2 + 0.60)) * (v1 * (tmp + 0.84 / tmp + 0.41)))
    data[tid] = v0
